description:
In this week's mini-episode, a listener asks Kate and Doree for advice on balancing household chores with a partner who's over-worked. They also discuss hair maintenance routines and what to do when your wedding makeup feels like too much.

To leave a voicemail for a future mini-ep, call 781-591-0390. You can also email the podcast at forever35podcast@gmail.com.

Theme music by Riot.
